\mathbb{R}^n
d(x,y)=d((x_1,\ldots x_n),(y_1,\ldots,y_n)) 
= \sum_{i=1}^{d}\lvert x_i-y_i\rvert = \sum_{i=1}^{d}\lvert y_i-x_i\rvert 
= d((y_1,\ldots y_n),(x_1,\ldots,x_n))=d(y,x)
|x-y|=|y-x|
x,y\in\mathbb{R}
x,y\in\mathbb{R}
x-y\geq 0
|x-y|=x-y
y-x\leq 0
|y-x|=-(y-x)=x-y=|x-y|
x-y\leq 0
|x-y|=-(x-y)=y-x
y-x\geq 0
|y-x|=y-x=|x-y|
|x-y|=|y-x|
